description: Ryan Jordan just finished his baseball practice and needs a massage to relax those worked muscles. He calls his handsome stepbrother Tannor Reed, because what is more relaxing than getting a handsome man massaging you. But this time things will be different because Tannor tells him he can meet him at his studio but family discounts are over. So Ryan thinks, 'well if I am paying full price this time I might as well get stepbrother dick included in the package.'
title: Stepbrother's Massage
